name: COMMONWEALTH Ex Rel., Robert FEHNEL, Petitioner, v. David DIGUGLIELMO, Superintendent State Correctional Institution at Graterford, Respondent
name_abbreviation: Commonwealth ex rel. Fehnel v. Diguglielmo

parties: COMMONWEALTH Ex Rel., Robert FEHNEL, Petitioner, v. David DIGUGLIELMO, Superintendent State Correctional Institution at Graterford, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 25th day of July, 2007, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is granted and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus is denied without prejudice to seek relief from the Commonwealth Court.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
